{"tid":1981640,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"宵夜  腸粉三款","createTime":"2020-04-20T19:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T12:32:26.000Z","uid":62277,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7754be8203c46826c55526dcfa2f1dda976ae7db","tid":1981640,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T19:00:54.000Z","msg":"腸粉全部即叫即拉<br />\n即拉齋腸比一般來貨既腸粉滑<br />\n不過就無咗煙韌口感<br />\n兩者各有優點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZrVpVcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZrVpVcc.jpg&h=d8ce2d38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叉燒腸皮夠薄<br />\n但又唔會薄到無曬口感<br />\n叉燒鬆化，唔霉<br />\n如果加啲蔥就更好味<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PaxorkG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPaxorkG.jpg&h=4f686842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4XynGT8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4XynGT8.jpg&h=0afcd95b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牛肉腸都ok，足料<br />\n不過略為偏咸少少<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/21/025513_382a4d539ad27d2d1c7b6ea4b68d1f73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F21%2F025513_382a4d539ad27d2d1c7b6ea4b68d1f73.jpg&h=e2e68e8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81cb86d13bf4eab806f673fd567e2aba77264780","tid":1981640,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T19:03:56.000Z","msg":"覺得飲茶一定要乜腸乜腸<br />\n宵夜就齋腸"},{"pid":"7449034705b63d5cb7ed4df893c69b08279a83e4","tid":1981640,"uid":274789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T19:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb1051fb88224697b28876950c727e67690e793","tid":1981640,"uid":152262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T19:05:16.000Z","msg":"多麻醬！！！"},{"pid":"adc3f4a65db05a77cfbc30230cbf3454873fcded