=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n何洪記只食過干炒牛河<br />\n正斗腸粉同細蓉都ok<br />\n不過真係貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T21:38:37.000Z","msg":"跑馬地正斗腸粉係好耐之前已經唔得了，d皮好厚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:35:40.000Z","msg":"正斗我係食開沙田<br />\n不過多數食細蓉<br />\n食過一次炸両腸"},{"pid":"20a5a2493262859f0c1118a7188d37269ea48944","tid":1981640,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"da26969da841ed3d9b6a7206605f705013b3c94c","tid":1981640,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T22:34:33.000Z","msg":"多麻醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:37:05.000Z","msg":"麻醬落多啲都唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3bb3b2e4d4d9ed65a0cfae07204e2753618974e","tid":1981640,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:47:47.000Z","msg":"腸粉其實係廣東先叫做手藝,啲垃圾式推腸粉根本不值一提...<br />\n但由於有黃店係呢隻...我食過一次...好彩係佢啲豉油較得幾好...腸粉都不老算係值返,但其實真係貴囉對我呢啲老嘢嚟講..<br />\n我細時食腸粉係响架度任我揀碟靚既先攞...又足料又平又好食...啲後生恨都恨唔到...要怪就怪你果代啲老豆老母,苦爸苦媽將你地掟去麥記食垃圾泥膠雞粒當一餐,仲話已經對你地好好...搞到啲茶樓執撚晒!<br />\n<br />\n而家反而係啲大陸落嚟學藝既救返廣東腸粉...真係不勝稀虛..<br />\n繼續食埋啲中國味道垃圾推腸粉啦...仲要幾十蚊兜,唔話你有病都笑你ON9!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2432649e090c465dd72a887375a9fec2822b3e74","tid":1981640,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:50:17.000Z","msg":"好肚餓"},{"pid":"f6fa7ba42f9a1b333fdd624a9fce75ccae625c64","tid":1981640,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3bb3b2e4d4d9ed65a0cfae07204e2753618974e","tid":1981640,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"202